mgwrap\"><img src=\"https://okuigumi.co.jp/saiyo-career/wp/wp-content/themes/try-csh/img/top/kv01.jpg\" alt=\"メインビジュアル\"></span></figure>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"kv__swiper--item swiper-slide\">\n              <figure class=\"kv__img\"><span class=\"swiper__imgwrap\"><img src=\"https://okuigumi.co.jp/saiyo-career/wp/wp-content/themes/try-csh/img/top/kv02.jpg\" alt=\"メインビジュアル\"></span></figure>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"kv__swiper--item swiper-slide\">\n              <figure class=\"kv__img\"><span class=\"swiper__imgwrap\"><img src=\"https://okuigumi.co.jp/saiyo-career/wp/wp-content/themes/try-csh/img/top/kv03.jpg\" alt=\"メインビジュアル\"></span></figure>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"kv__swiper--item swiper-slide\">\n              <figure class=\"kv__img\"><span class=\"swiper__imgwrap\"><img src=\"https://okuigumi.co.jp/saiyo-career/wp/wp-content/themes/try-csh/img/top/kv04.jpg\" alt=\"メインビジュアル\"></span></figure>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"swiper-pagination\"></div>\n      </div>\n\n      <h2 class=\"kv__copy font-min\">\n        <span class=\"txt txt01\">誇りで夢を叶える</span>\n        <span class=\"txt txt02\">プロフェッショナル集団。</span>\n      </h2>\n\n      <!-- 第２フェーズ公開 求人バナー ▼-->\n      <!-- <p class=\"kv__bnr\">\n          <span class=\"kv__close--btn ps-a\"><i class=\"fa-solid fa-x\"></i></span>\n          <a href=\"#\"><img src=\"https://okuigumi.co.jp/saiyo-career/wp/wp-content/themes/try-csh/img/top/top_bnr.png\" alt=\"求む!施工管理士 建築士・設計士\"></a>\n        </p> -->\n      <!-- 第２フェーズ公開 求人バナー △-->\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <section class=\"greeting section ps-r\" id=\"greeting\">\n    <div class=\"inner\">\n      <div class=\"gre__txtwrap wr-vt\">\n        <h2 class=\"gre__copy color-ma font-min fs-40 lh-2\">\n          採用メッセージ\n        </h2>\n        <h3 class=\"gre__copy02 fs-30 font-min02\">\n          「運ぶ」「預かる」<br>\n          「備え付ける」の<br>\n          　奥井組です。\n        </h3>\n        <p class=\"gre__txt\">\n          当社は昭和<span class=\"num\">29</span>年の創業以来、<br>\n          お客様に質の高いワンストップサービスをお届けするべく尽力し、<br class=\"spnone\">\n          着実に事業を拡大して参りました。<br>\n          奥井組には、人生に於ける第<span class=\"num\">2</span>、<br class=\"spnone\">\n          第<span class=\"num\">3</span>のフィールドに相応しい、<br class=\"spnone\">\n          あなたがこれまで培ってきた<br class=\"spnone\">\n          「情熱とパワー」を、更に大きく膨らませ存分に活かせる環境があります。<br>\n          様々な夢を叶えて<br class=\"spnone\">\n          次の時代へ技術を運び受け継ぎ、<br class=\"spnone\">\n          子供たちの未来を豊かにするべく、<br class=\"spnone\">\n          共に進み続けましょう。\n        </p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <section class=\"about ps-r\" id=\"about\">\n    <figure class=\"about__bg\"><img src=\"https://okuigumi.co.jp/saiyo-career/wp/wp-content/themes/try-csh/img/top/bg_about.jpg\" alt=\"バックグラウンド\"></figure>\n    <h2 class=\"about__ttl ps-a\"><img src=\"https://okuigumi.co.jp/saiyo-career/wp/wp-content/themes/try-csh/img/top/about_logo.png\" alt=\"奥井組を知る\"></h2>\n    <div class=\"about__txtwrap ps-a\">\n      <p class=\"about__txt fs-18 bold mb-40 color-wh\">奥井組は、昭和29年の創業以来、ワンストップサービスを実現するべく着実に事業を拡大してきました。そんな私たちの事業に懸ける想いやこれまでの道のり、環境への取り組み姿勢などをお伝えします。</p>\n      <p class=\"about__btn font-en\"><a class=\"link__btn\" href=\"https://okuigumi.co.jp/saiyo-career/about/\">VIEW\n          MORE<i class=\"arw fa-solid fa-chevron-right\"></i></a></p>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <section class=\"person section bg-gr  ps-r\" id=\"person\">\n    <div class=\"person__flex flex jc-between\">\n      <div class=\"person__left\">\n        <div class=\"person__left--inner\">\n          <h2 class=\"person__ttl  wr-vt font-min02 color-ma ps-a\"><span class=\"large\">人</span>を知る</h2>\n          <p class=\"person__ttl-en font-en color-ma fs-20 mb-30 lh-1\">PERSON</p>\n          <p class=\"person__txt fs-18 mb-40 \">\n            若手からベテランまで、<br>\n            奥井組で働く現役社員に入社のきっかけから日々の仕事内容ややりがい、<br>\n            そして未来への展望について聞きました。\n          </p>\n          <p class=\"person__btn font-en\"><a class=\"link__btn white\" href=\"https://okuigumi.co.jp/saiyo-career/person/\">view more<i class=\"arw fa-solid fa-chevron-right\"></i></a></p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"person__right\">\n        <div class=\"person__atcwarp flex  ps-r\">\n          <article class=\"person__atc atc01 swiper-slide\">\n            <a href=\"https://okuigumi.co.jp/saiyo-career/person/voice01/\">\n              <figure class=\"person__img\"><img src=\"https://okuigumi.co.jp/saiyo-career/wp/wp-content/themes/try-csh/img/top/person_img01.jpg\" alt=\"スタッフ\"></figure>\n              <div class=\"person__txtwrap flex jc-between\">\n                <h3 class=\"person__h3 fs-20\">\n                  <span class=\"position fs-14 block\">物流部門</span>\n                  <span class=\"font-min\">佐藤 竜二</span>\n                </h3>\n                <p class=\"person__arw\">\n                  <img src=\"https://okuigumi.co.jp/saiyo-career/wp/wp-content/themes/try-csh/img/cmn/link_arw_wh.png\" alt=\"矢印\">\n                </p>\n              </div>\n            </a>\n          </article>\n          <article class=\"person__atc atc03\">\n            <a href=\"https://okuigumi.co.jp/saiyo-career/person/voice02/\">\n              <figure class=\"person__img\"><img src=\"https://okuigumi.co.jp/saiyo-career/wp/wp-content/themes/try-csh/img/top/person_img02.jpg\" alt=\"スタッフ\"></figure>\n              <div class=\"person__txtwrap flex jc-between\">\n                <h3 class=\"person__h3 fs-20\">\n                  <span class=\"position  fs-14 block\">運輸部門</span>\n                  <span class=\"font-min\">岡本 順一</span>\n                </h3>\n                <p class=\"person__arw\">\n                  <img src=\"https://okuigumi.co.jp/saiyo-career/wp/wp-content/themes/try-csh/img/cmn/link_arw_wh.png\" alt=\"矢印\">\n                </p>\n              </div>\n            </a>\n          </article>\n          <article class=\"person__atc atc0